column5: Yah.. I guess I'll get home from there quicker than you! LOL  GCD... WATERPROOF satelitte tracking devices on all valuables this year! lol
Have a great summer Guys. Drive safe and of course boat safe. See you in Sept.
Have a good one Wayne.  Play safe, have fun, and take lots of pics!  Sinker

Take care Wayne hope you and your family have a great one up there lucky bugger,maybe we can chase a few Muskies together when ya get back,and Ive gotta talk to ya about some rivits for a lund I picked up recently
Have a great one Wayne (you lucky dog  ).
Have   a great summer to you & your family wayne,and catch lots of fish,and oh ya take lots of pics too !!!!  lol..lol   cheers
Have an awesome summer and I hope the fishing on Temagami is great for you this summer. Enjoy!!  Cheers B
You aint left yet?Go on...git! Joe
LOL Joe ! 10 hours bud.. 10 hours.

hey wayne..its almost time...well you have a great trip to gods country....man i wish i was going up with you...im 20 days away and believe me its not soon enough....keep those lines tight and the booze a flowing and always remember a day fishing adds another day to your life....

Have a great summer up north Wayne, and then lemme know if you need some ballast in your boat again once the snow starts blowin on GBay.  I'll bring the samiches  I'll be solo at Lakair in June Wayne, so if you decide to drop in and want to get out on the water for awhile, I've got a seat for you plus an extra musky pole & all the baits.
Have a great Summer Wyane and Leah.
I couldn't of said it better myself Glen!!.....  Wayne,  We should be at the lake by 7:00PM Friday....I'll give you a ring as we get to the access rd..
Adios amigo!
Make sure to velcro your camera to yer chest and have a great time bud! Oh, and congratulate Leah for me, for catching the biggest fish of the summer... off the dock! HH

Wishing everyone a great "warm" season of fishing !  Most of all play safe and don't get complacent. I know all too well how stuff can go to hell in a handbasket REALLY quickly without planning!  Oh and enjoy the extra bandwidth... OFC should run faster in about 24 hours! lol  It's time to take my sweetheart to God's country! I'll try to check in from time to time. Those that have it... use it... the number that is.  Doesn't look like we'll make Lakair at this point. Kevin couldn't do anything for us it appears...but we may drop in and bum a boat spot on the Saturday if anyone will have us aboard.  Cheers, Wayne
enjoy. maybe see ya in the fall.

This is what I call a head start Wayne Nothing wrong with the idea...and yes I'll probaly use it in few months Have a very fishfull summer and please leave some for me would you  Cheers, Ice Fisherman

Have a great summer Wayne (and Leah of course).  Hope it's filled with great memories!  If you're smart you won't give Bly your number....Leah and Bly may just talk the summer away in one phone call....LOL.  Hope to see you at some point!
I'll put a timer on the phone line in the junction box outside.
Have a fun and healthy summer Wayne and Leah!!!  Maureen
Have a great summer Wayne !  Be safe !
have a good one Wayne!
Best of luck to you and Leah !
Enjoy your summer and once again thank you for your advice over the past winter.
hope ya guys have a great summer, catch lots of fish, but most of all enjoy each other and all that mother nature has to offer.  jason
Have a great summer Wayne. Hopefully I'll see you in August.
Have a great time!! Hope you catch tons of fish.
You have yourselves a fantastic summer!
have a good one wayne we will try and keep the post counts going for ya  Cant wait for teh end of summer report hope this summer is a great one for ya.  mike
Have a great summer.  Hope you can stop in for the day and say howdy agan.
Don't forget to tether all of your valuables and pay attention to the fishin' lessons TMH is gonna give ya!
Have good one Wayne... lets hook up this summer!
Enjoy your summer!

Wayne'r Have a good one and I expect a crap load of reports from you this summer! I'll PM you my number and let you know how I make out @ you're sisters place. Say hi to Leah for me, Be safe and have fun!  G
Sheesh, you best drop by Lakair, I always have a spot for you in my boat. That aside, I hope you both have a great summer. Praps I'll get a chance to drop in on my return from Nipigon.
Have a Fantastic summer Bud!!! Hope we can hook up somewhere this summer.  Be safe and Have FUN!!
